OL,3,GYorkshire & Humber
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FCloudy in
OL,6,Fthe west, but more variable cloud in
OL,7,Fthe east will give a few clearer
OL,8,Fspells overnight. Risk of a few
OL,9,Fisolated showers, mainly over the
OL,10,FPennines. Breezy at times with
OL,11,Ftemperatures around average.
OL,12,
OL,13,CSaturday:FBecoming cloudy through the
OL,14,Fmorning with showers, these will
OL,15,Flikely ease during the afternoon with
OL,16,Fsunny spells developing. Clear periods
OL,17,Fovernight may allow for a patchy frost
OL,18,Fto develop.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
