OL,3,GYorkshire & Humber
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Sunday to Tuesday:FDrier
OL,6,Fand sunnier with winds easing Sunday.
OL,7,FCloudier on Monday with showers
OL,8,Fspreading inland from coastal areas.
OL,9,FDrier on Tuesday with sunny spells.
OL,10,FDaytime temperatures around average
OL,11,Fbut chilly overnight.
